               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Dāwit "Psalter" (fols. 2r-151ra)
 I-1) Mazmura Dāwit "Psalms of
                     David" (fols. 2r-115v)
 I-2) Maḥālǝya nabiyāt "The Canticles of the
                     Prophets" (fols. 115v-127r)
 I-3) Maḥālǝya maḥālǝy "Song of Songs" (fols.
                     127v-134r)
 I-4) Wǝddāse Māryām “Praise of Mary” (fols. 135ra-146vb)
                     I-5) Anqäṣä bǝrhān “The Gate of Light” (fols. 146vb-151ra)
 
 Additio
                     1.</summary>
